{"tid":493080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★驚見長袍女白影　港鐵柴灣車廠鬧鬼？","createTime":"2017-12-08T07:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T08:29:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"98256aeab624b6c51fc3ad8f7f0f38135df6e7f3","tid":493080,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171208/photo/bkn-20171208091402911-1208_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171208093338\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171208091402911-1208_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171208093338&h=c417a591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵柴灣車廠鬧鬼？近日網上流傳鬧鬼圖片，有人繪影繪聲指深夜時分柴灣港鐵車廠，有車廠維修技工目擊一名身穿白袍的白影，披頭散髮站在車廠一無人路口動也不動。網上留言稱，當時有技工直指見鬼，嚇得躲在技工室內不敢外出，更即時向廠長匯報。<br />\n<br />\n從該張流傳圖片放大後所見，隱約見到相片中出現一個有腳人形白影，將手放在背後，站在室內車廠一處空地上。圖片帶有描述指：「長髮到腰着白袍企喺路口唔郁」當時有技工以為見鬼，嚇得手足無惜，更指曾向廠長匯報。事件隨即在不少港鐵車長群組流傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171208/bkn-20171208091402911-1208_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171208%2Fbkn-20171208091402911-1208_00822_001.html&d=UYGkvbzWySGVpgnXueqqfNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f594056c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171208/bkn-20171208091402911-1208_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cb3d0106cc941e1423ba23e1cc0a323ff6119efa","tid":493080,"uid":19454,"like":246,"dislike":6,"score":240,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:33:25.000Z","msg":"may be游b<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/235401_b2c880d4c7e06ec318a2158a534e17f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F235401_b2c880d4c7e06ec318a2158a534e17f5.jpg&h=6ee2c7c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0e797985e070995254a995378e1a5f82572c8b5","tid":493080,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:3